com.sonf.core.filter

类 IFilterAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sonf.core.filter.IFilterAdapter
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    IFilter
    直接已知子类:
    ProtocolFilter

    public class IFilterAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFilter
    An adapter class for IFilter. You can extend this class and selectively override required event filter methods only.
